Last one imma do for a while.
Hope u see it
Feel it & share it
It’s all blood & sweat for me.
Something i made
hope u could feel the difference.
#COMEALIVE
#MAGICMAN 

LINK IN BIO.

Thanks to my fam
@v1nh

.
We prepped this literally less than a week from zero.
In different studios with million ideas…
With everyone having a different schedule, was difficult to gather all together.
But We still managed to puzzle everything up and arrange it together.
It was nightmare again…N we made it happen
I really want to say thank you to all these five amazing individuals and true family that was there for me.
U all inspired me so much
And thanks for being there in the journey.
I love you all 🙏🥷⚔️🎬🎞️

#MAGICMAN album out now everywhere.
Blue music video out now.
Gave everything I got to this point in my life.
Also Im shooting come alive MV now.
.
I really don’t know what to say cuz it’s been such a journey.
The audience and my crowd who started with me since day1 will know what we all went through. And thanks for thinking it’s worth it loving me.
Along the journey , Thanks to all the pain, struggle& obstacles through the peaks and valleys of what i experience in my career, in the industry. mentally, physically & personally.
No one believed in me but you all. 
I have been living a life of getting denied everyday in a lot of ways.
And i always think I should just be better and I hope that one day my work will speak for itself. That’s why I always say I’m not satisfied with myself & I just need to be better and better. So that I can truly make you all, my people proud one day.
.
I just wanna be honest with my crowd, my audience. To you all.
This is me. 
The music, the lyrics, the delivery, the attitude, color, tone… etc
This is me and I feel like MAGIC MAN. 
.
MAGIC MAN is more of a feeling and abstract, like the ultimate form of one self, having gone through different peaks and valleys of life to arrive at the most authentic version. Everyone goes through low points in their lives personally mentally, Trust your gut feeling get up and move forward, go for your dream , never rely on anyone else because it’s not their dream. always trust your gut feeling, be U.
Everyone is able to become their own form of MAGIC MAN.
Plz take a bit of time and listen to it
Can you relate to it ? 
.
Hope you enjoy my blood and sweat all over the years,
I hope my work can translate to your friends and family that you share to.
Listen to the album,
If you like the album, you would really like to see me and my performance. I will fight for a performance in your countries & cities.
Lmk down below. 
.
This is Jackson Wang.
This is MAGIC MAN.
If this is not it,
I don’t know what is anymore.
.
#jacksonwangBlue 
Thank u for believing in me

10 years in this❤️
Ups and down , peaks and valleys.

Good don’t mean it’s always good.
Bad dont’t mean it’s always bad.

It’s all bubbles and we still doing what we love.
Happy and blessed that we were a part of everyone’s journey.
We moved on individually, artistically & the bond we started will never end.
Fam is fam. Brothers are brothers.
Stay true and honest.
Everyone 2024 be happy and healthy.
Find ur happiness.
Be real and honest to urself.
Find u cuz no one will do it for u.
Find it and do it.
Promise me.
Find u.
